Since Gmail no longer supports direct login with your normal password for apps, you must use an App Password.

Go to your Google Account Security page.

Enable 2-Step Verification.

Open Google App Passwords.

Select:

App: Mail

Device: Other â†’ Name it BulkMailer

Copy the 16-character password Google gives you.

Use this App Password in the Streamlit app instead of your normal password.

Gmail Sending Limits:

Free Gmail: 500 emails/day.

Google Workspace: 2,000 emails/day.
